thread.title: Kirsty B
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Kirsty B

author: Kirsty B
title: Kirsty B
text: There was a great range of combinations with the ink for our printer ie individuals and different combinations all at great prices. The website was super easy to use. The ink was delivered in a very timely manner and is of tope quality. I highly recommend Ink Station. We were very impressed and will be repeat customers.
